Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:32.98,Hackadoll_Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,251)}Episode 2: "Please Let Us Be Idols!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:32.43,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:34.49,Hackadoll_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.99,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Triple booking? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:39.20,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth booking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:43.53,quadruple,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The correct phrase is "quadruple booking."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:42.90,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Guess I screwed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:44.45,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.04,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Solving messes like this is \Nwhat makes a great producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:50.29,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,What's three or four events? \NI can fill this schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.04,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,No, I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.60,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:55.29,Hackadoll_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't fill this last slot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:58.18,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,If only there were an agency that could \Nintroduce me to an idol who's free...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.05,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,What you need is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:03.26,Hackadoll_Main,123,0000,0000,0000,,The Personal Entertainment AI \Nthat syncs to you: HackaDoll!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.90,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,H-HackaDoll?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.81,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,The AI that can advance \Nany part of a person's life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.46,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're here, you can rest at ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.56,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,We will be in the event that has an opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:16.03,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You weren't going to \Nintroduce me to an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.57,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.28,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.04,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.67,Hackadoll_Main,2,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.54,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.58,Hackadoll_Main,3,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be idols?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:29.01,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wear cute costumes, sing, dance, \Nmake everyone go "squee!" for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.33,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,It's every girl's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.34,Hackadoll_Main,2,0000,0000,0000,,I think {\i1}you{\i0} just want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.34,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the offer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.73,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:43.01,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,I promise we'll advance your company,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.60,Hackadoll_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so please let us be idols!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.60,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to trouble the sponsor—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.85,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us be idols!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.35,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a very important event—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.35,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Let us be idols!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.61,Hackadoll_Main,2,0000,0000,0000,,There are a few days left until the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.14,Hackadoll_Main,2,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd just give us a chance \Nand let us prove ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.35,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.27,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Let us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.99,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:07.48,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start you off with some lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.10,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.98,agency,1,0000,0000,0000,,IWS\NIdol Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.73,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.75,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0000,0000,0000,,And so, our days of taking lessons began.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.53,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0000,0000,0000,,Running...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.05,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0000,0000,0000,,Hopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.40,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0000,0000,0000,,Hand-shaking practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.06,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0000,0000,0000,,Photo sessions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.26,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.82,hackadolls,Bold Text,0000,0000,0000,,Ikebukuro Girls CD Shop                  {\b1}HackaDolls{\b0}                  Autograph Signing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:35.99,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,might just work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.43,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the big day is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.03,Hackadoll_Main,2,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.07,Hackadoll_Main,3,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.80,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Today's event {\i1}is{\i0} very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.79,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Special?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.30,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The winner of today's event
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:54.61,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,gets to release a debut CD \Nfrom a major record label.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:58.71,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,What?! D-Debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.93,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Only if you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.80,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:08.39,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time. Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.81,hackadolls2,1,0000,0000,0000,,18:00~18:30         HackaDolls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.81,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.24,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm really nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:22.43,Hackadoll_Main,Mob idol,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear? There's a \Nlast-minute replacement today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.80,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean the group that \Nclaims they can "advance" people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.36,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 2,0000,0000,0000,,They're making a mockery of idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.24,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 3,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.97,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 4,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't really get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:34.27,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 5,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they won't get great results.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:39.11,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,But we worked really hard for this!\NI know we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.67,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe the audience \Nwon't be satisfied with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.57,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be an idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.73,Hackadoll_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but if the audience doesn't get excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:51.31,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,then I can't advance the producer's career...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:55.85,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if anyone will even watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.00,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.17,Hackadoll_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Producer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.33,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,All idols struggle with that insecurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:09.69,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the miracle of overcoming \Nthat insecurity to stand on the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.62,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,that the audience is here to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:17.33,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already excited to see what kind \Nof miracles you girls will perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.92,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how badly you wanted to be an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.34,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,And you want to advance my career, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.61,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:31.00,Hackadoll_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there'll be people watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:33.61,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go make miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.00,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.41,Hackadoll_Main,2,0000,0000,0000,,We're still in the girls' bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.33,Hackadoll_Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.33,Hackadoll_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,HackaDolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.21,Hackadoll_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Last-minute filler?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.29,Hackadoll_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.27,Hackadoll_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who can "advance" anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.48,Hackadoll_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.65,Hackadoll_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,So they can be idols, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:49.95,Hackadoll_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.20,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you all! We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.95,Hackadoll_Main,123,0000,0000,0000,,HackaDolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:59.00,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,We practiced lots to become idols today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.98,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to our song, \N"Cabbage Testing"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.51,cabbagesanction,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,435)}Cabbage Testing\N{\fs12}Lyrics: Ikuo Geso\NComposition: Daisuke Horita
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.58,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0000,0000,0000,,These vibrations...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.99,Hackadoll_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The building itself is resonating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:09.08,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Did I mess up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.03,Hackadoll_Main,Otaku 1,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.83,Hackadoll_Main,Otaku 1,0000,0000,0000,,#1-chan, you were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.45,Hackadoll_Main,Otaku 1,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul reached me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:20.96,Hackadoll_Main,Otaku 1,0000,0000,0000,,It was the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.71,Hackadoll_Main,1,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
